msg: Follow up to r26402: do not pass -std=c89 to the C++ compiler to
remove the following warning from the JavaHL compile:
cc1plus: warning: command line option "-std=c89" is valid for C/ObjC

except for not adding -std=c89 to CXXFLAGS.
Set using the value from configure.
